{
  "text": "Presence of canal aberrations has been evaluated according to the parameters of Thompson and Dummer [CITATION_1] by a third operator blinded for this study. Thanks to photographic evaluation has been recorded the possible presence of: elbow, apical zip, perforation and danger zone. In addition, we evaluated if experience factor could increase the rate of instrument fracture when using ProTaper or WaveOne systems. ",
